Elvish XDG
============

###### A module to return XDG directories.

```elvish
epm:install github.com/chlorm/elvish-xdg
use github.com/chlorm/elvish-xdg

$xdg:xdg_cache_home
$xdg:xdg_config_home
$xdg:xdg_data_home
$xdg:xdg_desktop_dir
$xdg:xdg_documents_dir
$xdg:xdg_download_dir
$xdg:xdg_music_dir
$xdg:xdg_pictures_dir
$xdg:xdg_prefix_home
$xdg:xdg_publicshare_dir
$xdg:xdg_runtime_dir
$xdg:xdg_templates_dir
$xdg:xdg_videos_dir
```
